---
title: "EDGE Service Areas | Texas Home Energy Solutions"
description: "EDGE serves homeowners throughout Texas with complete home energy solutions. Find microgrid and battery backup services in Houston, Dallas, Austin, San Antonio, and more."
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> Service Areas</nav>
    <h1>Serving All of Texas</h1>
    <p>EDGE delivers energy independence to homeowners across the Lone Star State.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header fade-up">
      <span class="section-label">Major Metro Areas</span>
      <h2>Find EDGE in Your City</h2>
      <p>Select your city to learn about local energy challenges and how EDGE can help.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="locations-grid">
      <a href="{{ '/locations/houston/' | url }}" class="location-card fade-up">
        <h4>Houston</h4>
        <p>Greater Houston Area, Harris County, Fort Bend, Montgomery</p>
        <span class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</span>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ '/locations/dallas/' | url }}" class="location-card fade-up">
        <h4>Dallas</h4>
        <p>Dallas County, Collin County, Denton County</p>
        <span class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</span>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ '/locations/austin/' | url }}" class="location-card fade-up">
        <h4>Austin</h4>
        <p>Travis County, Williamson County, Hays County</p>
        <span class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</span>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ '/locations/san-antonio/' | url }}" class="location-card fade-up">
        <h4>San Antonio</h4>
        <p>Bexar County and surrounding areas</p>
        <span class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</span>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ '/locations/fort-worth/' | url }}" class="location-card fade-up">
        <h4>Fort Worth</h4>
        <p>Tarrant County and surrounding areas</p>
        <span class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</span>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ '/locations/el-paso/' | url }}" class="location-card fade-up">
        <h4>El Paso</h4>
        <p>El Paso County</p>
        <span class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</span>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ '/locations/plano/' | url }}" class="location-card fade-up">
        <h4>Plano</h4>
        <p>Collin County</p>
        <span class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</span>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ '/locations/frisco/' | url }}" class="location-card fade-up">
        <h4>Frisco</h4>
        <p>Collin & Denton Counties</p>
        <span class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</span>
      </a>
      <a href="{{ '/locations/the-woodlands/' | url }}" class="location-card fade-up">
        <h4>The Woodlands</h4>
        <p>Montgomery County</p>
        <span class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header fade-up">
      <span class="section-label">Why Local Matters</span>
      <h2>Built for Texas Conditions</h2>
      <p>EDGE systems are specifically engineered for the unique challenges Texas homeowners face.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card fade-up">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Extreme Heat</h4>
        <p>Our battery systems are rated for Texas summers, with thermal management to maintain performance in 100°+ temperatures.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 17.58A5 5 0 0 0 18 8h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 4 16.25"/><line x1="8" y1="16" x2="8.01" y2="16"/><line x1="8" y1="20" x2="8.01" y2="20"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/><line x1="12" y1="22" x2="12.01" y2="22"/><line x1="16" y1="16" x2="16.01" y2="16"/><line x1="16" y1="20" x2="16.01" y2="20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Severe Weather</h4>
        <p>Designed to withstand hail, high winds, and flooding conditions common across Texas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card fade-up">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>ERCOT Grid</h4>
        <p>Optimized for the Texas grid's unique characteristics and interconnection requirements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <div class="container fade-up">
    <h2>Don't See Your City?</h2>
    <p>We serve homeowners throughout Texas. Contact us to confirm service in your area.</p>
    <a href="{{ '/contact/' | url }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Check Availability →</a>
  </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
